Trump ta West Virginia yakin neman zabe lokaci, YouTube tashar
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump zai kaddamar da taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na taron Trump a cikin taro biyar da aka shirya a makon gobe, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yayin da aka dakatar da zaben da zai tabbatar da wanda ya zaɓa don cike gibin kotun koli saboda akwai haɗarin cewa 'yan Republican za su rasa goyon bayan majalisa a lokacin zaben a watan Nuwamba, Trump ya yi niyyar samun goyon baya ga zaben ta wucin gadi.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya samun damar yin hakan ta yanar gizo?
Taron Trump na Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 a 7pm ET.
Za a iya ganin taron Trump na West Virginia a kai tsaye a YouTube a hanyar haɗin da ke ƙasa.
Trump ya shirya dage zaben tabbatar da majalisar dattawa na mako guda a kan zargin da ake yi a gaban kotun koli game da lalata a karkashin FBI a kan Brad Concentration a wannan makon.
Amma babban burin taron shine samun goyon baya ga 'yan Republican da za su yi takara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, duk tarurrukan shugaban kasa Trump guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, "suna nufin ƙarfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya don kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen 'yan Republican a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Dattijai", in ji Reuters.
"Shugabancin majalisa yana da mahimmanci a gare shi, don haka a cikin wannan yanayin aiki, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu", in ji Trump, wanda ya ƙi ambaci wani kakakin yakin neman zabe, ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya taron a Wembano Stadium a Wheeling, West Virginia Metro News Agency ta ce, a yau da dare za a yi taron "da masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da za su iya samun bayanai daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh".
A wannan Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata, jihar da ta lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump na neman goyon bayan dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi rashin nasara a zaben.
