HIV/AIDS: An gano cewa kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin mutane sun kamu da cutar a kasar Sin
Kasar ta ce yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar ta China ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce an samu mutane sama da 820,000 a kasar.
A cikin kashi na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai, an samu kusan mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Yawancin sababbin mutane suna da rashin tsaro na jima'i a baya.
A baya, an yi amfani da jini da aka yi amfani da shi wajen yaduwar cutar ta HIV a wasu yankunan ƙasar Sin.
Amma, a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce, an rage yawan kamuwa da cutar HIV kusan gaba daya.
Koyaya, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu zuwa mutane 100,000.
A cikin LGBT na kasar Sin, an samu karuwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i.
A shekarar 1997 an kawar da tsarin gay a kasar Sin, amma LGBT suna samun karbuwa.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ƙa'idodin tsayayyen ƙasar, maza 70 zuwa 90% na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure a ƙarshe.
Sau da yawa, ana kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar yin jima'i a hanyoyi marasa lafiya.
Tun daga shekarar 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ce ta yi amfani da maganin HIV don samunsa ga kowa.
