A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival a birnin New York, inda za a yi bikin da ke nuna yadda taurari masu ban sha'awa za su yi tafiya da kuma yadda za a kawar da talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai da aka yi bikin Global Citizen, za a ga dubban mutane suna tattaruwa a babban filin tsire-tsire na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin abubuwan da Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shavan Mendes suka yi ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
An bayyana bikin Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 a matsayin fadada shirin Global Poverty Project (Tsarin kawar da talauci a duniya), wani kungiya mai ba da shawara ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen ta ta ta hanyar kara yawan masu yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti na kyauta don taron (idan ba ku yarda ku biya tikitin VIP ba), masu halartar kide-kide dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka ko "aikin" da suka haɗa da aikin agaji, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya, ko kuma shiga wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ke samu ke nan, da yake har yanzu yana da shekaru 12 kafin ya kai ga burinsa?
