A cewar wani sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka, Ryan Ginge, Washington na iya tura rundunar jiragen ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don hana Rasha samun makamashi zuwa kasuwannin da ke cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zhengyi ya zargi cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, musamman ma a inda take aiki a kan kira na gwamnatin da ta dace, dalili ne na karya don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Abin da ya sa suke cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son samar da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabas ta Tsakiya a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin magance wannan.
"Amurka tana da ikon bude hanyoyin ruwa ta hanyar rundunar ta, kuma ta hana su shiga cikin kasuwar makamashi idan ya cancanta", in ji shi.
